### Auth Service API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8001

### 1. Health Check - Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8001/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Health Check - Specific Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8001/health/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. User Signup
POST http://localhost:8001/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser1",
    "email": "test1@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

###

### 4. User Signup - Another User
POST http://localhost:8001/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser2",
    "email": "test2@example.com",
    "password": "securepassword456"
}

###

### 5. User Login - Correct Credentials
POST http://localhost:8001/auth/login?username=testuser1&password=password123
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 6. User Login - Wrong Password
POST http://localhost:8001/auth/login?username=testuser1&password=wrongpassword
Content-Type: application/json

###

